- Email (ID 786) is checked
- Phone (ID 792) is checked

Now I need to apply these changes. Looking at the available buttons in the dropdown, I can see there's a 'Cancel' button (ID 861) and a 'Reset' button (ID 859). Let me check if there's any other button that might apply the changes. I don't see one, so I'll try to click on the 'Columns' button again to close the dropdown and apply the changes.
